WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
Hi, thanks for considering RStudio Server Pro or Shiny Server Pro.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:07.000
If you're someone who uses the free and open source RStudio IDE,

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:12.000
and possibly the R package of Shiny and RMarkdown along with the free and open source Shiny Server,

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:18.000
or you're an IT colleague of theirs and you're curious to know why companies like those listed at the bottom of our website homepage

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:23.000
upgraded from our free and open source products, you've come to the right place.

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:25.000
So let's get to the heart of it.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:30.000
For some people, it's as simple as the desire to help us pay for our contributions to the open source R community.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:32.000
We appreciate that.

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:37.000
For others, it's because your legal advisors would rather you use a commercial license than the AGPL.

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:42.000
Or it's because you'd rather get support directly from us rather than the community alone.

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:48.000
But for many more, it's because your IT team needs visibility into how the IDE and Shiny apps are being used.

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:54.000
Statistics, logs, audits, health checks, and metrics that can roll up into standard reporting systems.

00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:59.000
And for the most people, it comes down to features that help you scale your adoption of R and RStudio products.

00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:04.000
For example, both RStudio Server Pro and Shiny Server Pro provide security features

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:09.000
that help you fit into your existing identity and data security practices,

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:15.000
and performance features that let you monitor and control the compute resources used by developers and applications.

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:17.000
So there you have it.

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:21.000
All good reasons why people just like you buy RStudio Server Pro and Shiny Server Pro.

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:23.000
Thank you for considering them for your organization.

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:26.000
We hope you'll take a deeper dive into our website now.

